  <brief_title>Intraperitoneal Mesh-Implementation After Laparotomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intraperitoneal Mesh-Implementation After Laparotomy to Reduce Risk of Incisional Hernia: a Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
