  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the study is to evaluate the risk reduction of intraperitoneal mesh-implementation
      after laparotomy (Group 1) in a randomized control trial compared with patients with standard
      abdominal closure (Everett-suture). This is the primary endpoint. Second endpoints are the
      feasibility of mesh-implementation even after colorectal surgery, find risk factors for wound
      infection and incisional hernia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
